column1: EXPERIMENTAL DESIGN: In this study all of the major members of the matrix metalloproteinase ( MMP - 1, MMP - 2, MMP - 3, MMP - 7, MMP - 9, MMP - 13, MT1 - MMP and MT2 - MMP) / tissue inhibitor of matrix metalloproteinase ( TIMP - 1, TIMP - 2, and TIMP - 3) system have been investigated by immunohistochemistry in a series ( n = 90) of stage III ( Dukes ' C) colorectal cancers.
